Package com.stardevllc.stardata.api.interfaces

Interface Database

All Known Subinterfaces:
SQLDatabase
All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractSQLDatabase, H2Database, MySQLDatabase, PostgresDatabase, SQLiteDatabase
public interface Database
Represents a generic database, only really used for SQL based things for now.
See SQLDatabase for more information.

    • get

      <T> List<T> get(Class<T> clazz, String[] keys, Object[] values) throws Exception
      Gets Objects of the class provided. This will still return a list even if it is just one
      The two arrays must match each other in both length and what you want to do. The index of the first one will map to the index of the second one.
      Type Parameters:
      T - The type of the table
      Parameters:
      clazz - The class of the table
      keys - The Array of Columns to base the query on. This must match the values
      values - The array of values based on columns. This must match the columns
      Returns:
      The list of objects that Match. This should never return a null object. If there is nothing that matches, it will be an empty list.
      Throws:
      SQLException - Any SQL errors that happen
      Exception
